This project, completed entirely inside After Effects (no prerendered 3d), is perfect for showcasing all your family photos. From pictures of your ancestors up to your most recent precious moments, this project will showcase all your memories in a sentimental light. The length of this video can be adjusted to whatever you need, from 5 seconds up to nearly 20 minutes. With up to 158 shots and far more image placeholders than I care to count, you will have no shortage of places to put your images. Each shot has 3 instances, most with unique camera moves.
